sentences: Jessica Georganne Pilnäs, (born 5 July 1978 in Åryd, Växjö ), is a Swedish singer perhaps mostly known for her song "Jag ger dig allt" (English: I give you all).
She sang the song in Melodifestivalen 1995, and came in third place.
In 2000, Her song, "Pretender", which she recorded under the name Isa, also became a hit single in Sweden.
Born in Åryd, she is the daughter of Thommy Gustafsson, keyboard player for the Swedish band Sven-Ingvars.
